Package net.gravitydevelopment.updater

Defines the BukkitDev update utility for plugins (not used by this branch)

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Updater.UpdateCallback
    Called on main thread when the Updater has finished working, regardless of result.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Updater
    Check for updates on BukkitDev for a given plugin, and download the updates if needed.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Updater.ReleaseType
    Represents the various release types of a file on BukkitDev.
    Updater.UpdateResult
    Gives the developer the result of the update process.
    Updater.UpdateType
    Allows the developer to specify the type of update that will be run.
